  <brief_title>An Observational Study in Type 2 Diabetic Patients on Oral Antidiabetic Drugs and Basal Insulin in Near East Countries</brief_title>
  <acronym>BO2NE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Multicentre, Multinational, Open Label, Non-controlled, Observational, 24-week Study in Patients Using Oral Anti-Diabetic (OAD) Drugs + Levemir® (Insulin Detemir) for Treatment of Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus in Near East Region Countries</official_title>
