  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Asia. The aim of this observational study is to investigate the
      safety and efficacy of insulin detemir as add-on therapy in type 2 diabetic patients who are
      using oral antidiabetic drugs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
